3) Office Products - The card reader can add productivity to a home or office PC, making it suitable for the office products category.

4) Camera & Photo - The card reader supports various memory card formats commonly used in cameras, making it relevant to the camera and photo category.

5) Tools & Home Improvement - Although less likely, the card reader can be installed into a desktop computer, which could be considered a home improvement task.

The Rosewill RCR-IM5001 card reader is designed to install neatly into an open 3.5” drive bay on your desktop to give you convenient access. This 5-slot reader supports CF, SD, MMC, MS, M2/MICRO SD and extreme digital cards....
